Aim:- WRITE A PROGRAM TO DEMONSTRATE CLASS AND OBJECT IN PYTHON

ALGORITHM:-
STEP 1: start the program
STEP 2: create a class Student
STEP 3: define method to get student details (name, USN, marks)
STEP 4: define method to calculate total marks
STEP 5: define method to display student details
STEP 6: create an object of the class
STEP 7: call methods to input, calculate and display data
STEP 8: stop the program

CODE:-
